"{\"uid\": \"menshealth.com-fitness-a61638743-matt-anderson-volleyball-olympics-training\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"After ironing out some kinks, the Olympic vet is confident as the Opening Ceremonies approach.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 94, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some kinks\", \"from\": 18, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic vet\", \"from\": 30, \"to\": 45}, {\"ngram\": \"the Opening Ceremonies\", \"from\": 62, \"to\": 84}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This story is part three ofMen's Health's\\\"Road to the Olympics\\\" series, where six athletes share their training journeys as they prepare to compete at the 2024 Paris Olympics in July.\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This story\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 106}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 114}, {\"ngram\": \"three ofMen\", \"from\": 115, \"to\": 126}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\\\" series\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 166}, {\"ngram\": \"six athletes\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 186}, {\"ngram\": \"their training journeys\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read all of the athletes' entrieshere.\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes' entrieshere\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WE JUST LANDEDin Poland yesterday.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9885995429760692, \"rank\": 0.01147981008930624, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have two friendly matches left here, and then it's on to Paris.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999999840702, \"rank\": 1.5929905564496092e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two friendly matches\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We get in on the evening of July 22, and then we have athlete processing the next day, where we get all the new gear and stuff from the sponsors.\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the evening\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"all the new gear\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"the sponsors\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's always a fun part [of the Olympic process].\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fun part\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic process\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then we will have a few trainings to be able to iron stuff out.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few trainings\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 652}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will only get one training session on the competition court before match play starts on the 27th.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one training session\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition court\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"match play\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 763}, {\"ngram\": \"the 27th\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And hopefully we play the entire Olympics.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the entire Olympics\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pool play at the VNL competition did not really go as we'd hoped.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pool\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"the VNL competition\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We did not make it to the finals.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It really showed us that we are not where we need to be yet.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We definitely had glimpses of where we want to be as a team.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"glimpses\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we also saw a couple things we needed to work on.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a couple things\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think physically we look pretty good, but we just were not playing the best volleyball.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best volleyball\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of our guys were pretty beat up, battling injuries.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"our guys\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"battling injuries\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not allow us to go as hard.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So when it came to actually performing, we just were not as sharp as we want it to be.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are making the proper adjustments, though, and that makes me feel better about our performance.\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the proper adjustments\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1415}, {\"ngram\": \"our performance\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me personally, I am the type of player that when things are not working as well, or are as sharp as we want them to be, I put my head down and want to work hard until it's all flushed out.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the type\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"player\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All of these changes are things we know we can do, and things we have done in the past regularly.\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these changes\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So getting back to doing it just requires the adequate amount of training reps, from my perspective.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the adequate amount\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"training reps\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"my perspective\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like I said last time, I have been trying to stay positive in terms of our performance.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"our performance\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think part of practice is being somewhat analytical-I need to be able to criticize myself and check in on what I can do better.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2092, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1975}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But competition is about being a little more free-flowing and less critical, which is kind of a counterintuitive approach compared to the way I view practice.\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"kind of a counterintuitive approach\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So striking that balance takes time.\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that balance\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think these friendly matches on Saturday and Sunday are going to be a great indicator of how I am feeling both on and off the court.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these friendly matches\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"a great indicator\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By not making the finals at VNL, though, we got an extra weekend at home.\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"VNL\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2456}, {\"ngram\": \"an extra weekend\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2489}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That gave us some more time to train.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2511}, {\"ngram\": \"some more time\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We might not be perfect on the court, but I feel like we are in a really good spot when it comes to team chemistry.\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"a really good spot\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2619}, {\"ngram\": \"team chemistry\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have had a lot of team meetings and have really grown together.\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"team meetings\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am definitely starting to really feel the emotions of it all.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have this awesome opportunity to go for greatness in our sport.\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this awesome opportunity\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2817}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To me, the Olympics is the best trophy to win in our sport.\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2872}, {\"ngram\": \"the best trophy\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So there is a lot of pressure and a lot of stress and anxiety, for sure.\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think we have everything in place to set us up to play our best.\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Want to follow more Olympians' journeys?\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more Olympians' journeys\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Click below to read about their training methods, wellness routines, and more.\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their training methods\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3147}, {\"ngram\": \"wellness routines\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE Cori Ritchey, C.S.C.S., is the fitness editor atWomen's Health, as well as a certified strength and condition coach and group fitness instructor.\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3190, \"end\": 3194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cori_(lunar_crater)\", \"score\": 0.5240624774231717, \"rank\": 0.7949999999998612, \"text\": \"Cori\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cori_(lunar_crater)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cori_(lunar_crater)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"C.S.C.S.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3211}, {\"ngram\": \"atWomen\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3242}, {\"ngram\": \"Health\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's reported on topics re